HEADWORD: Kalmuck
<hw>Kal"muck</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<pluf>pl.</pluf> <fld>(Ethnol.)</fld> <def>See
<er>Calmucks</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
